    • complement

      public static <X> Set<X> complement(Set<X> set1, Set<X> set2)
      Calculates the relative complement of set2 in set1 as a new set. Set2 does not have to be a subset of set1.
      Type Parameters:
      X - shared type of elements of either set.
      Parameters:
      set1 - the first set
      set2 - the second set
      Returns:
      A set containing all elements that were in set1 but not in set2
